[s]I'm currently trying to add all types of clipping on my server and I'm going to need the Clip and World folders that are required. I was wondering if anyone had these folders and could perhaps reupload them for me.
I know I could download a few sources to scavenge them, but that is wasting precious bandwidth. Thanks. [/s]
